Code:

class StringIsNumeric {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        
        String input = "123";
        boolean bool= false;
        
        for(int i=0; i<input.length();i++)
        {
            char c = input.charAt(i);
            
            if(Character.isDigit(c))
            {
                bool = true;
            }
            else
            {
                bool = false;
                break;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(bool);
        
    }
}

Output:
true
